installation package for irys 2.2.0 

This package has been tested on Debian 7.5 only

this package requires following packages : 

openjdk-7-jre tomcat7 postgresql

Notes :
- oracle jre 7 can be used instead of openjdk one
- postgresql version 9.x required

to install irys server, download irys-chouette-server.deb and install it :

  dpkg -i irys-chouette-server.deb

follow instructions after installation

to update, remove previous version before install new one
   - created user and database are preserved